data.description:
This 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a standout with its upgraded features and thoughtful enhancements. The interior boasts modern touches such as granite countertops in the kitchen, under cabinet lighting, and beautiful hardwood floors in the main living areas. The spacious living room with 9-foot vaulted ceilings and dimmable can lights creates a welcoming atmosphere.   Motivated Seller!!

The master bedroom is a retreat with dual walk-in closets, offering ample storage space. Additionally, the second bedroom also features walk-in closets, providing convenience and organization. Originally a 3-bedroom home, the garage has been converted into two additional bedrooms or versatile office spaces while maintaining storage capacity.

Outside, the property shines with upgraded lighting in the garage and soffit, as well as an expanded covered patio that enhances outdoor living space. The large backyard area provides room to relax and entertain. Extra parking space and an electric RV hook-up add practicality and convenience for homeowners with recreational vehicles.

Located just 5 minutes from Choctaw Casino and 15 minutes from Lake Texoma, this home offers easy access to entertainment and outdoor activities. Its proximity to highways ensures quick travel to Texas, making it a convenient location for commuters. With its blend of upgraded features, functional spaces, and great location, this home presents a wonderful opportunity for comfortable living and enjoyable experiences.
